## üí° Tip: Use ChatGPT as a Temporary Code Lab Assistant

You can copy and paste full Python files into ChatGPT to get live analysis, refactors, and debugging help ‚Äî just like a pair programmer.

‚úÖ Totally legal ‚Äî as long as it‚Äôs your code (or permissively licensed)  
‚úÖ Session-aware ‚Äî ChatGPT can remember your pasted files for the whole conversation  
‚úÖ No training risk ‚Äî Your code stays private; nothing is used to train the model

‚ö†Ô∏è Session memory resets when you refresh, log out, or start a new chat  
‚ö†Ô∏è Don‚Äôt paste private or proprietary code unless you‚Äôre sure it‚Äôs safe

